race.description: Newman Mcdonnell Memorial Grade 5 Series H Pr1 Div
race.comment: BOURNE FRANKY (3) could manage only second but ran fast time (29.90) at this track over 512m. Has the ability and expected to go close again. DIRTY DASH (6) copped a check in the run and finished out of the placings when sixth (26.43) at Murray Bridge over 455m in a Grade 5. Rates a key player and gets chance to atone. OREGON CALDWELL (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (30.08) last time in a Other at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Key runner on best form. TATTOOIST (7) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
